snippet.title: Croc Legend of the Gobbos coming April 2nd!
snippet.description:
The wait is nearly over!  🎉🎉

We’re thrilled to announce that the highly anticipated remaster of Croc Legend of the Gobbos is launching April 2, 2025! 🐊💚

Wishlists are open for PC on GOG, with Nintendo Switch, PlayStation, and Xbox digital storefronts following soon.
